{\an1}(sighs)

30:08.932 --> 30:10.391
{\an3}Once you've
exhausted your anger,

30:10.475 --> 30:12.852
{\an3}you'll end up
like Alexa.

30:15.480 --> 30:18.525
{\an3}We have to help each other.
