I mean,<i> all</i> of this. Uh...

35:06.604 --> 35:07.522
(laughs)

35:07.605 --> 35:09.190
We're fine.

35:09.273 --> 35:11.984
We are in no danger.

35:12.902 --> 35:14.821
None of this is real.

35:14.904 --> 35:15.863
<i>None of this is real.</i>

35:15.947 --> 35:16.948
{\an5}(alarm blaring)

